{"tid":2478394,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"元朗中槍少年暴動罪成 蘇文隆判入教導所","createTime":"2021-04-07T04:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T05:28:59.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"28f2610e9d3d5a2b895671b098310762adae24b5","tid":2478394,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:34:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14820&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=02cbc42d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14820</a><br />\n<br />\n#粉嶺裁判法院第二庭 #少年法庭<br />\n#蘇文隆主任裁判官 #判刑<br />\n👤15歲手足 #1004元朗 <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1) 有意圖而導致他人身體受嚴重傷害<br />\n被告被控於2019年10月4日元朗大棠路及青山公路元朗段交界與其他不知名人士意圖非法及惡意導致警員1877 陳港橋Chan Kong Kiu 身體受嚴重傷害。<br />\n<br />\n(2) 暴動<br />\n被告被控於2019年10月4日元朗大棠路及青山公路元朗段交界與其他不知名人士參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n＊被告承認控罪(2)，控方表示撤回控罪(1)並存於法庭檔案內。<br />\n<br />\n詳情請參考蘋果日報報導： <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210320/SZSI7VH24FGQNNZS5EAQHJJRUU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210320%2FSZSI7VH24FGQNNZS5EAQHJJRUU%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=3eb6c226\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210320%2FSZSI7VH24FGQNNZS5EAQHJJRUU%2F&h=0abfc074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210320/SZSI7VH24FGQNNZS5EAQHJJRUU/</a> <br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n‼️判入教導所並留有刑事紀錄‼️<br />\n<br />\n（感謝臨時直播員報料）"},{"pid":"4b9f5224264884462d9799d376f3492c6ce5b89c","tid":2478394,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T04:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac